_extent&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:1},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;cat&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:1},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;cat-1500&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:1},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;cool roofs&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:12},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;park shade&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:18},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;street trees&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:5},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;street trees + cool roofs&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:12},{&#92;&quot;intervention&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;street_trees_achievable_test&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:1}]&quot;' data-total-rows='10' data-size-bytes='433' data-total-columns='2' data-max-columns='50' data-banner-text='&quot;&quot;' data-pagination='false' data-page-size='10' data-field-types='[[&quot;intervention&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;count&quot;,[&quot;integer&quot;,&quot;int64&quot;]]]' data-show-filters='true' data-show-download='true' data-show-column-summaries='false' data-show-data-types='true' data-show-page-size-selector='true' data-show-column-explorer='true' data-show-chart-builder='true' data-row-headers='[]' data-has-stable-row-id='false' data-lazy='false' data-preload='false'></marimo-table></marimo-ui-element><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>By time of day:</strong></span></span><marimo-ui-element object-id='nWHF-2' random-id='4eecce44-5412-506e-6f18-c255b32a9bf8'><marimo-table data-initial-value='[]' data-label='null' data-data='&quot;[{&#92;&quot;time_of_day&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;1200&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:16},{&#92;&quot;time_of_day&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;1500&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:31},{&#92;&quot;time_of_day&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;1800&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;count&#92;&quot;:16}]&quot;' data-total-rows='3' data-size-bytes='103' data-total-columns='2' data-max-columns='50' data-banner-text='&quot;&quot;' data-pagination='false' data-page-size='10' data-field-types='[[&quot;time_of_day&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;count&quot;,[&quot;integer&quot;,&quot;int64&quot;]]]' data-show-filters='true' data-show-download='true' data-show-column-summaries='false' data-show-data-types='true' data-show-page-size-selector='false' data-show-column-explorer='true' data-show-chart-builder='true' data-row-headers='[]' data-has-stable-row-id='false' data-lazy='false' data-preload='false'></marimo-table></marimo-ui-element><marimo-callout-output data-html='&quot;&#92;u003cspan class=&#92;&quot;markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents&#92;&quot;&#92;u003e&#92;u003cspan class=&#92;&quot;paragraph&#92;&quot;&#92;u003e&#92;u003cstrong&#92;u003eNo population, vulnerability, or demographic COG rasters found for Cape Town.&#92;u003c/strong&#92;u003e All COGs are UTCI (thermal comfort index) rasters. They cover baseline conditions and multiple intervention scenarios across 3 times of day (1200, 1500, 1800) and several spatial masks \u2014 but the underlying measurement is always thermal stress, not population exposure or vulnerability.&#92;u003c/span&#92;u003e&#92;u003c/span&#92;u003e&quot;' data-kind='&quot;warn&quot;'></marimo-callout-output></div>"
