        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/html": "<div style='display: flex;flex: 1;flex-direction: column;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: normal;flex-wrap: nowrap;gap: 0.5rem'><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"user-priorities-data-availability\">User priorities \u00d7 data availability</h3></span><span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Section A</strong> maps the four example priorities from the product concept. <strong>Section B</strong> adds priorities that the available Cape Town data actually enables \u2014 framed as user goals the system could credibly support today.</span></span><marimo-ui-element object-id='ZHCJ-0' random-id='6ee3bde8-fc1d-ad93-2d45-c1c9150cdd70'><marimo-table data-initial-value='[]' data-label='null' data-data='&quot;[{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;A &#92;&#92;u2014 from product concept&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Reduce extreme heat exposure&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;UTCI baseline + scenario delta COGs&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Yes&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;None&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;A &#92;&#92;u2014 from product concept&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Protect vulnerable populations&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;high_risk_utci_pct scalar only&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;District&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;No&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Need population/vulnerability raster (e.g. WorldPop)&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;A &#92;&#92;u2014 from product concept&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Increase tree canopy&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;tree_cover_* scalars only&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;District&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;No&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Need tree canopy raster (e.g. open canopy dataset)&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;A &#92;&#92;u2014 from product concept&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Maximise impact per budget&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Scenario delta COGs (impact side only)&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel (impact only)&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Partial&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Cost data entirely absent &#92;&#92;u2014 must be user-supplied&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;B &#92;&#92;u2014 enabled by available data&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Where would street trees cool the most?&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;street_trees COG deltas (1200, 1500, 1800)&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Yes&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;None&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;B &#92;&#92;u2014 enabled by available data&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Where would cool roofs have the highest impact?&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;cool_roofs COG deltas (1200, 1500, 1800)&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Yes&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;None&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;B &#92;&#92;u2014 enabled by available data&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Where is heat stress worst at peak afternoon?&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;UTCI baseline COG at 1500&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Yes&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;None&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;B &#92;&#92;u2014 enabled by available data&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Which intervention cools the most in my selected area?&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Delta COGs for street trees, cool roofs, park shade, combinations&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Yes&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Requires zonal stats over multiple COGs &#92;&#92;u2014 computationally feasible&#92;&quot;},{&#92;&quot;section&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;B &#92;&#92;u2014 enabled by available data&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;user_priority&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;How does combined street trees + cool roofs compare to either alone?&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;data_available&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;street_trees_cool_roofs combined delta COGs exist&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;granularity&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Pixel&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;custom_aoi_viable&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;Yes&#92;&quot;,&#92;&quot;gap&#92;&quot;:&#92;&quot;None&#92;&quot;}]&quot;' data-total-rows='9' data-size-bytes='2261' data-total-columns='6' data-max-columns='50' data-banner-text='&quot;&quot;' data-pagination='false' data-page-size='10' data-field-types='[[&quot;section&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;user_priority&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;data_available&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;granularity&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;custom_aoi_viable&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]],[&quot;gap&quot;,[&quot;string&quot;,&quot;str&quot;]]]' data-show-filters='true' data-show-download='true' data-show-column-summaries='false' data-show-data-types='true' data-show-page-size-selector='true' data-show-column-explorer='true' data-show-chart-builder='true' data-row-headers='[]' data-has-stable-row-id='false' data-lazy='false' data-preload='false'></marimo-table></marimo-ui-element></div>"
